<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Change in the Status of Your Application to the <span tal:replace="site">Site Name</span></title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Evolution of Your Application</h1>
    
    <p>Hello <span tal:replace="user">Applicant's Name</span>,</p>
    
    <p>Your application on the platform <span tal:replace="site_url">URL</span> as a <span tal:replace="candidature_type">Role</span> 
    <span tal:condition="python:candidature.state == CandidatureState.APPROUVED">has been accepted</span>
    <span tal:condition="python:candidature.state == CandidatureState.REJECTED">has been rejected</span>
    <span tal:condition="python:candidature.state not in [CandidatureState.APPROUVED, CandidatureState.REJECTED]">is under processing and has changed its status</span>
    .
    </p>
    
    <p>Here are the details of its evolution:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Candidature ID: <span tal:replace="python:Candidature.oid">Application ID</span></li>
        <li>Transition Date: <span tal:replace="python:Candidature.modifications[-1]">Last transition</span></li>
        <li>New Status: <span tal:replace="python:Candidature.state">New application status</span></li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>Thank you for your participation.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The team of <span tal:replace="site">Site Name</span></p>
</body>
</html>
